  {
    title: 'Account responsibility',
    body: 'If you create an account, you are responsible for keeping your login details secure and for activity that happens through your account.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Content and trademarks',
    body: 'FIFA World Cup, FIFA+, and other third-party names or marks belong to their respective owners. IPTV World Cup is not presented as FIFA+ or as an official FIFA website.',
  },
  {
    title: 'No guaranteed availability',
    body: 'Streaming quality and availability can depend on internet connection, device support, plan terms, content rights, regional restrictions, and service conditions.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Contact',
    body: 'For questions about these terms, use the contact method provided at checkout or in your account area. This page is a general website terms template and should be reviewed by a qualified legal professional before production use.',
